description: Returns information about an MLflow Tracking Server.

parameters.name: TrackingServerName
parameters.description: The name of the MLflow Tracking Server to describe.

nested_items.name: TrackingServerArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the described tracking server.

nested_items.name: TrackingServerName
nested_items.description: The name of the described tracking server.

nested_items.name: ArtifactStoreUri
nested_items.description: The S3 URI of the general purpose bucket used as the MLflow Tracking Server artifact store.

nested_items.name: TrackingServerSize
nested_items.description: The size of the described tracking server.

nested_items.name: MlflowVersion
nested_items.description: The MLflow version used for the described tracking server.

nested_items.name: RoleArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for an IAM role in your account that the described MLflow Tracking Server uses to access the artifact store in Amazon S3.

nested_items.name: TrackingServerStatus
nested_items.description: The current creation status of the described MLflow Tracking Server.

nested_items.name: TrackingServerMaintenanceStatus
nested_items.description: The current maintenance status of the described MLflow Tracking Server.

nested_items.name: IsActive
nested_items.description: Whether the described MLflow Tracking Server is currently active.

nested_items.name: TrackingServerUrl
nested_items.description: The URL to connect to the MLflow user interface for the described tracking server.

nested_items.name: WeeklyMaintenanceWindowStart
nested_items.description: The day and time of the week when weekly maintenance occurs on the described tracking server.

nested_items.name: AutomaticModelRegistration
nested_items.description: Whether automatic registration of new MLflow models to the SageMaker Model Registry is enabled.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the described MLflow Tracking Server was created.

nested_items.name: CreatedBy
nested_items.description: Information about the user who created or modified an experiment, trial, trial component, lineage group, project, or model card.

nested_items.name: UserProfileArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the user's profile.

nested_items.name: UserProfileName
nested_items.description: The name of the user's profile.

nested_items.name: DomainId
nested_items.description: The domain associated with the user.

nested_items.name: IamIdentity
nested_items.description: The IAM Identity details associated with the user. These details are associated with model package groups, model packages, and project entities only.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM identity.

nested_items.name: PrincipalId
nested_items.description: The ID of the principal that assumes the IAM identity.

nested_items.name: SourceIdentity
nested_items.description: The person or application which assumes the IAM identity.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the described MLflow Tracking Server was last modified.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedBy
nested_items.description: Information about the user who created or modified an experiment, trial, trial component, lineage group, project, or model card.
